fully.' => '資料庫變更已成功應用。','Ok' => '好的','Dismiss' => '解僱','Fluid Checkout database update' => 'Fluid Checkout 資料庫更新','Some changes to the database are required. As with any update, we recommend you to <strong>take a full backup of your website before proceeding</strong>.' => '需要對資料庫進行一些更改。與任何更新一樣，我們建議您<strong>在繼續之前對您的網站進行完整備份</strong>。','Update database' => '更新資料庫','Fluid Checkout is not compatible with the Divi Builder checkout layout' => 'Fluid Checkout 與 Divi Builder 結帳佈局不相容','<p>Fluid Checkout needs the classic WooCommerce shortcode-based checkout form to work. When using the Divi Builder to customize the look and feel of the checkout page, the classic shortcodes are replaced with custom widgets from the Divi Builder for each part of the checkout page. These custom widgets are not compatible with Fluid Checkout.</p><p>Please edit your checkout page replacing the Divi Builder widgets with the a text widget containing the shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>.</p>' => '<p>Fluid Checkout 需要經典的基於 WooCommerce 短代碼的結帳表單才能運作。當使用 Divi Builder 自訂結帳頁面的外觀時，經典的短代碼將被來自 Divi Builder 的針對結帳頁面每個部分的自訂小工具所取代。這些自訂小部件與 Fluid Checkout 不相容。</p><p>請編輯您的結帳頁面，用包含短代碼<code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>的文字小工具取代 Divi Builder 小工具。</p>','Edit the checkout page' => '編輯結帳頁面','Read the documentation.' => '閱讀文檔。','Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature needs to be disabled when using Fluid Checkout' => '使用 Fluid Checkout 時需要停用 Germanized PRO 多步驟結帳功能','When using Fluid Checkout, the multistep feature from the Germanized PRO plugin becomes unnecessary and can cause <strong>critical errors while processing new orders</strong>. Please disable the Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature in the plugin settings.' => '當使用 Fluid Checkout 時，Germanized PRO 插件的多步驟功能變得沒有必要，並且可能<strong>在處理新訂單時導致嚴重錯誤</strong>。請在插件設定中停用 Germanized PRO 多步驟結帳功能。','Go to Germanized settings' => '轉到德語設定','Thanks for choosing Fluid Checkout!' => '感謝您選擇 Fluid Checkout！','You have been using the plugin for a while now. How do 